  "status": "Review",
  "summary": "This proposal introduces an attribute of ownership and profit share quantities for each token under an NFT. This attribute signifies a stake in the ownership and profit rights associated with the NFT's specific privileges, enabling the querying, transferring, and approval of these shares, thereby making the shares represented by each token applicable in a broader range of use cases.",
  "title": "ERC-721 Ownership Shares Extension"
